cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with synthesizing a light field from a single image using deep neural networks. The paper also involves geometric reasoning, which is a common theme in computer graphics (cs.GR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed model also uses novel loss functions, which are related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM).
